# Agent Instructions

This project uses platform-builder. Load the skill before any work.

## Rules

1. Read `docs/SESSION.md` first — it's where we are
2. One ticket per session
3. TDD — tests first
4. Before every commit: run `scripts/verify.sh`, fix all failures
5. Manual verify: applicable STANDARDS.md checklists + all docs (term consistency, no contradictions, no stale docs)
6. Update `docs/SESSION.md` after every session
7. `scripts/verify.sh` exits non-zero → blocked. Fix everything before proceeding.
